com.ibm.team.enterprise.buildablesubset.common.dto

Interface IBuildableSubsetCriteria2

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBuildableSubsetSubsetCriteria2, IBuildableSubsetWorkItemCriteria2

    public interface IBuildableSubsetCriteria2
    Criteria are methods or objects that contribute files to a subset. For example a work item can be used to populate a subset, and doing so creates an IBuildableSubsetWorkItemCriteria2.
    Since:
    6.0
